</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,693,1324]" pageId="1" pageNumber="10">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="10">
- Areoles of adaxial leaf surface not completely filled by bulla-based hairs, abaxial leaf surface visible, bulla-based hairs mostly restricted to veins, appressed or slightly spreading, flowers pedicellate, petals clawed, anthers with dorso-basal appendage to 
<quantity box="[477,558,1269,1292]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="10" unit="mm" value="0.3">0.3 mm</quantity>
long, calyx teeth reflexed in fruit, restricted to Massif du Nord, 
